│ **Understanding the Issue**: The bug occurs when transforming               │
│ `shufflevector` of two `icmp` instructions with different predicates that   │
│ match via `CmpPredicate::getMatching`. Specifically, `icmp samesign ugt`    │
│ and `icmp sgt` match (canonicalizing to `sgt`), but the transformation      │
